## Portfolio projects

### 1. HR Onsite Workforce & Leadership Analytics

**Goal:** Provide leadership with timely, accurate visibility into onsite workforce percentages, leadership engagement, and employee distribution across regions to support real estate and HR decisions. [file:21]  

- Consolidates workforce analytics across multiple countries into centralized Tableau / Visier dashboards.  
- Highlights onsite vs remote percentages, leadership engagement trends, and regional headcount distribution.  
- Includes scenario views for office utilization and space planning.  

[View project →](./projects/hr-onsite-workforce-analytics/README.md)

---

### 2. HR Attrition, Retention & Forecasting

**Goal:** Improve retention decisions by detecting data quality issues, automating refreshes, and forecasting attrition risk and onsite participation. [file:21]  

- Automated data validation checks to reduce reporting errors and improve trust in executive dashboards.  
- Daily refresh of attrition data to cut response time from weeks to under 48 hours. [file:21]  
- Predictive attrition analytics using relocation and workforce data to support proactive retention strategies. [file:21]  

[View project →](./projects/hr-attrition-forecasting/README.md)

---

### 3. Real Estate & Finance BI for Portfolio Management

**Goal:** Support finance teams with interactive reporting on real estate portfolios, CapEx, budgeting, and scenario analysis. [file:21]  

- Sample from 120+ Tableau and Power BI dashboards built for portfolio management and forecasting. [file:21]  
- Focuses on utilization, CapEx tracking, and budget vs actual with drill-downs by property and time.  
- Demonstrates KPI design, stakeholder-focused views, and performance optimization in BI tools.  

[View project →](./projects/real-estate-bi-finance/README.md)

