### 4. Freelancing Marketplace Analytics (Upwork-style)

**Goal:** Identify market trends and in-demand skills using data from millions of freelancers to guide strategic planning. [file:21]  

- Recreates an R/Python-based analytics project using large-scale marketplace data. [file:21]  
- Analyzes category growth, skill demand, and pricing trends with visual summaries.  
- Includes recommendations for product, marketing, or talent teams on where to invest.  

[View project →](./projects/freelancing-marketplace-analytics/README.md)

